  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the katsuramuki-cut onion and cook until it is lightly browned.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the shrimp and cook until they are pink and fully cooked.",
    "Add the cauliflower rice, shrimp stock, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper to the skillet.",
    "Stir everything together and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover the skillet, and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork and serve hot."
